headline: Cummins (NYSE:CMI) Unveils New Battery Energy Storage Systems In Middle East Expansion
summary: Cummins (NYSE:CMI) witnessed a notable price move of 8% last week, coinciding with the launch of their Battery Energy Storage Systems in Dubai. This advancement aligns with the company's strategy to address energy challenges and enhance grid stability in the Middle East. Additionally, the market overall saw a robust uptrend of 8.4%, partially fueled by gains in the energy sector.
